PrecisAuthority (a) for the Prime Minister or the Minister of Indian Affairs and Northern Development to enter into a FINAL FRAMEWORK AGREEMENT with the Province of Saskatchewan and a number of Indian Bands concerning the resolution of certain outstanding treaty land claims, and (b) for the Minister of Indian Affairs and Northern Development to enter into a COST- SHARING AGREEMENT with the Province of Saskatchewan and into INDIVIDUAL AGREEMENTS with 26 Indian Bands.
